    <text xml:lang="en">
      <body>
        <p>Within the framework of our project, all locations with epigraphic finds will be catalogued,
          and mapped with the help of the <ref target="http://pleiades.stoa.org/">Pleiades Project</ref>. In the meantime,
          the map below shows all locations in for the Northern Black Sea area, geolocated by
          the Pleiades Project and projected on Barrington Atlas map tiles in a Leaflet framework.
        </p>
        <div><divGen type="pleiadesmap"/></div>
